{"tid":1744524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就黎區選 要文宣宣傳下保皇黨幾年戰續","createTime":"2019-11-21T19:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T08:55:47.000Z","uid":143747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5703d2de360efbb8747c26d9b22e1225f9a71963","tid":1744524,"uid":143747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:06:33.000Z","msg":"其實好多老人家都會停低望下連儂牆 <br />\n而個時候就要貼下保皇黨戰績 例如加公屋租 1萬一條泊單車鐵柱 <br />\n大家上網搵到圖 send出黎等大家都可以襯而兩日貼文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4LQSWaV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4LQSWaV.jpg&h=05e808f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVcU9vW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVcU9vW.jpg&h=952828ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iGrF44g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiGrF44g.jpg&h=89ac85bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TbguYph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTbguYph.jpg&h=60a53124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3a217a48b1234db0fc7a874326fe2dfb15c3d44","tid":1744524,"uid":143747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EssudZv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEssudZv.png&h=63e96f50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1752a5cc601b4fd9cc2a8ac508677a5bb17f3650","tid":1744524,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:16:35.000Z","msg":"有用 推"},{"pid":"7dff20ca9909d01c8196147c0019fb55f27dfe0b","tid":1744524,"uid":143747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:34:48.000Z","msg":"大家得airdrop 又好<br />\n印出黎都好"},{"pid":"610d79c9f80b38fafcf41407013c970217207a05","tid":1744524,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:36:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a3e3e7e21e6dea33f2c8d7ae90a71e5f3e550fd","tid":1744524,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:39:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39fa22337d07d815a7d4f78d785bf9417e3f9783","tid":1744524,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:41:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36534c27a3ab1110be63de3de343ebe2cd73fcca","tid":1744524,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n收到風建制除左&quot;時間&quot;(呢2日吹到行既愈早投票愈好)仲有2招蠱惑野<br />\n<br />\n1) 搵啲揸拐扙老藍絲響去票站既樓梯/電梯頂住大家(有唔少票站得一條路去的)<br />\n博大家唔敢打人<br />\n解決方法<br />\na) 搵番老黃絲頂番住佢地,男頂男,女頂女<br />\nb) 後生巴絲她溫柔咁扶佢地快速行完條路,佢地一叫暈or唔舒服就夾手夾腳她溫柔咁抬佢走,又係男招呼男.女招呼女<br />\n<br />\n2) POPO講明會高調巡邏,收到風會每幾分鐘就埋去泛民街站查一次(佢真係有權咁做,好似一晚查酒吧4次牌咁)<br />\n解決方法<br />\n和理非最多係&quot;人&quot;,呢幾日去到區選,各區和理非可以組團去建制同偽黃侯選人街站,<br />\n用各種方式去令佢地全日唔得閒,e.g. 成團人全日車輪戰去同佢地傾同佢地拗,<br />\n但千萬唔好鬧,務求癱瘓建制同偽黃街站.記住,唔好一個人去,要成團咁去,<br />\n仲有,唔駛一團人做晒一日,和理非就係人多,幾團人磨佢一個街站都得<br />\n<br />\n區選唔好唔投,你點睇區選都好,只要係俾建制贏(只係贏就夠,唔駛大贏)<br />\n林鄭同POPO直頭可以大條道理出機關槍,所以一定要投,要正正經經咁投<br />\n<br />\n</span>"}]}